    Then stdout contains substring:
      """
      Livepatch is not available for Ubuntu <pretty_name>.
      """
    When I run `pro status --all` with sudo
    Then stdout matches regexp:
      """
      livepatch +yes +n/a +Canonical Livepatch service
      """

